    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Directs the Department of the Interior, for National Park System land, and the Department of Agriculture, for land under its jurisdiction, to require any film crew of five persons or fewer to obtain a permit and pay an annual fee of $200 to conduct commercial filming activities or similar projects on such land and waterways.</p>]]></text>
